      <title>随着耐克市场份额的流失，投资者担心相关性</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/nike-its-gotta-be-shoes-could-be-thing-past-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[耐克越来越依赖其标志性篮球鞋来提高销量，但随着这家运动服装巨头将市场份额流失给新品牌，一些分析师和投资者想知道这是否是一个错误。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/nike-its-gotta-be-shoes-could-be-thing-past-2024-03-21/</guid>
